						               													<description>Virus Veteran is a card game in which it is your goal to have less virus points than your opponents. The card game is split in two kinds of cards, action cards including tourists, mutations, veterans and more... and into standard virus cards. The standard cards will determine your number of points at the end!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;To gain the upper hand you can either use tourists and mutations to double the numbers of your opponents points, or you can use medics and lockdowns to block or annihilate aggressive cards of the other players. Bottlenecks and veteran cards allow you to draw cards from your opponents or to get rid of your own virus points.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The single cure card determines the end of the game and boosts your chance to win the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The cards are designed in a humoristic comic style which is inspired by the ongoing pandemic. I mean look at the toilet-paper hoarders, aren`t they perfect fitting joker cards?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
